text: Grubbenvorst is a village in the Dutch province of Limburg. It is part of the municipality of Horst aan de Maas. In 2021, 4,790 people lived there. It was an independent municipality until 2001. Category:Settlements in Limburg (Netherlands) Category:Former municipalities of Limburg (Netherlands) Category:Horst aan de Maas
